OL,3,CThames Water a 'disaster of a water
OL,4,Ccompany' say MPs after sewage spill
OL,6,FThames Water - the country's biggest
OL,7,Fwater supplier - has been described as
OL,8,Fa "disaster of a water company" by MPs
OL,9,Fduring a debate about its performance.
OL,11,FThe comments came as Oxford West and
OL,12,FAbingdon MP Layla Moran described the
OL,13,Fcompany's "shoddy performance" after
OL,14,Fit dumped sewage over thousands of
OL,15,Fhours last year.
OL,17,FShe called for the supplier to become
OL,18,Fa public interest company which would
OL,19,Fforce it to put its customers before
OL,20,Fprofits and clean up its act to
OL,21,Fprotect waterways.
