OL,6,FMs Moran said: "Across the network,
OL,7,FThames Water spilled sewage for 6,500
OL,8,Fhours in the last nine months of 2023.
OL,10,F"This pollutes our waterways, damages
OL,11,Fthe natural environment, and poses
OL,12,Fserious health risks to wildlife, pets
OL,13,Fand humans.
OL,15,F"We need radical action, we need to
OL,16,Fprotect our environment and we need to
OL,17,Fbring down people's bills.
