OL,6,FAn army of volunteers regularly take
OL,7,Fwater samples in rivers, including the
OL,8,FLoddon, to test for pollution.
OL,10,FStuart Singleton-White, The Angling
OL,11,FTrust, said: "We've done over 200
OL,12,Ftests across the year here on the
OL,13,FLoddon and we're getting that
OL,14,Fconsistent failure rate for phosphate
OL,15,Flevels.
