OL,6,F"While we've been doing those tests,
OL,7,Fon six incidents across the year,
OL,8,Fwe've also actually physically seen
OL,9,Fpollution in the Loddon and its
OL,10,Ftributaries flowing downstream while
OL,11,Fwe've been testing.
OL,13,F"So the Loddon has a serious problem
OL,14,Fand Thames Water really do need to
OL,15,Fstep up their action to protect this
OL,16,Freally important river."
