OL,6,FA spokesperson for Thames Water told
OL,7,Fus that action is being taken to
OL,8,Fimprove the health of rivers and it is
OL,9,Finstalling specialist equipment to
OL,10,Fremove phosphorus from its sewage
OL,11,Ftreatment works.
OL,13,FIt also acknowledges it has more to do
OL,14,Fto reduce pollution levels.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Environment
OL,17,FDepartment, Defra, said it is taking
OL,18,Fcomprehensive action through more
OL,19,Finvestment and tougher regulation.
